A fix for https://github.com/rusoto/rusoto/issues/893 . Some work to go still due to compilation warnings, but it appears to work.

Test case (`cargo test --features lambda -- --nocapture`):

```rust
#[test]
fn should_run_function() {
    let client = LambdaClient::simple(Region::UsWest2);
    let request = InvocationRequest {
        function_name: "rusototest".to_owned(),
        invocation_type: Some("Event".to_owned()),
        ..Default::default()
    };

    let result = client.invoke(&request).sync().unwrap();
    println!("{:#?}", result);
}
```

